com.st.st25sdk.type5

Class ReadBlockResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.st.st25sdk.type5.ReadBlockResult

  • public class ReadBlockResult
extends java.lang.Object
    Class containing the response of Iso15693 readBlocks() used for Type5 and Vicinity commands. blockSecurityStatus is initialized with 0xFF and is - set to 0 when a block is not locked - set to 1 when a block is read-only data is an array containing the block's data.
